Legal Contracts Manager
Inspire Selection
Dubai, UAE
Posted on: 29 Apr 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Our Client, an international energy company based in Dubai, is looking for a contracts manager to join their existing team.
The primary focus of the role is to play a leading role in the development and management of a solid legal support function that enables internal stakeholders to achieve business excellence. The incumbent will be working closely with the various functions and business divisions in order to support the corporate restructuring activities in the MENA region, prepare commercial agreements, roll-out processes, provide and coordinate timely support from external advisers.
REQUIREMENTS
QUALIFICATIONS:
•Excellent academic credentials and a Bachelor degree in Law from a recognized University
• 3 – 5 years of professional experience in a leading law firm and/or legal department of a multinational corporation
• Ability / maturity to deal with internal and external senior level executives within the organization
• Ability to understand the business goals, perspectives and exercise good judgments in a timely manner
• Flexible and proactive in approach, able to drive multiple-simultaneous initiatives
• Excellent communication and document drafting skills
• Results-oriented and able to work under pressure
• High degree of reliability, confidentiality, discretion, quality and professionalism
• Have a high level of integrity and good common sense
• Have strong ethics and values and be widely trusted, with the ability to establish and maintain effective relationships and gain confidence
• Native Arabic speaker and fluent in English. French would be an asset.
• Availability to travel for business meetings
ABOUT THE COMPANY
Inspire Selection employs highly knowledgeable, professional consultants who are experts in connecting the right people with the right opportunities.
Our reputation has been built upon our honesty, integrity and our ability to source candidates of the highest calibre right across our specialist sectors. As a result, we are recruitment partners to a wide spectrum of organisations - from leading blue chip companies to smaller, local businesses.
Sectors we cover include HR, Admin, Banking, Finance & Accounting, Emiratisation, Legal, Sales & Marketing, Technical & Construction.
Our client base is primarily in the UAE, but we also cater for other countries in the Middle East region.
